title: Grateful Dead - Europe '72, Vol. 22: 26.05.1972 > London
description:
Europe '72, Vol. 22: May 26th, Lyceum Theatre, London, England:

The last night. As much the band could be forgiven for being exhausted and ready to go home, they brought their A-game and played what many consider to be one of the top two or three shows on the tour.

The second, set, though, is so good that it was immortalized on Side 5 and Side 6 of the â€˜Europe '72â€™ album. What that album is missing from this jam, though, is a terrific â€˜Other Oneâ€™ around the â€˜Morning Dewâ€™, and the finest (and totally appropriate) â€˜Sing Me Back Homeâ€™ of the tour.
